				\begin{document}$${L}_i^v(X)=1{0}^{G_i^v(X)}, \space \forall \space X\in \Gamma, \space v\in [1\dots c], \space i\in [1\dots s]$$\end{document}</tex-math>
              <mml:math id="M46">
                <mml:msubsup>
                  <mml:mrow>
